title: Wisconsin Parties, Mannequins > Real People 5.15.20
itunes:title: Wisconsin Parties, Mannequins > Real People 5.15.20
description:
In episode 631, Jack, Miles, and Jamie are joined by Couples Therapy podcast's Andy Beckerman to discuss how outside may be the way to go for quarantine times, how to re-open America, diners using mannequins at tables, and more!

FOOTNOTES:

  1. Indoor transmission of SARS-CoV-2
  2. Quarantine Fatigue Is Real
  3. How to Reopen America Safely
  4. So small restaurants can open, some Cincinnati streets will close - and become outdoor dining spaces
  5. Diners at this reopening restaurant can get social with dressed up mannequins
  6. WATCH: Slum Village - Selfish feat. Kanye West & John Legend (junior state remix)
